          inner join partsupp
          on (supplier.s_suppkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
        inner join lineitem
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey > partsupp.ps_partkey)
      inner join orders
          inner join lineitem

        inner join part
              inner join partsupp
              on (part.p_comment = partsupp.ps_comment )
            inner join part
            on (partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey)
          inner join lineitem
              inner join customer
              on (customer.c_phone >= lineitem.l_linestatus)
            inner join customer
              inner join supplier
              on (customer.c_mktsegment = supplier.s_phone)
            on (lineitem.l_shipdate > lineitem.l_shipdate)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = supplier.s_acctbal )
        on (lineitem.l_shipdate >= lineitem.l_shipdate)
      on (customer.c_nationkey < supplier.s_nationkey)

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_commitdate
from 
  nation
    inner join lineitem
    on (nation.n_name = lineitem.l_returnflag )
where lineitem.l_suppkey is not NULL
limit 92;
nl: What are the commit dates for all orders that have a supplier and were returned?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_comment
from 
  supplier
    inner join part
        inner join nation
        on (part.p_retailprice > part.p_retailprice)
      inner join customer
      on (part.p_partkey > nation.n_regionkey)
    on (supplier.s_suppkey <= customer.c_custkey)
where part.p_mfgr is not NULL
limit 45;
nl: What are the comments from customers who have purchased parts made by suppliers in a specific region, along with other relevant details?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as money) as money)), 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost
from 
  partsupp
    inner join customer
    on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = customer.c_custkey )
where partsupp.ps_availqty is NULL;
nl: What are the market segments of customers who have no available quantity, along with their maximum supply cost and the highest possible supply cost?

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost
from 
  partsupp
        inner join part
          inner join partsupp
          on (part.p_mfgr = part.p_container)
        on (partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey )
      inner join customer
        inner join partsupp
                inner join partsupp
                on (partsupp.ps_partkey > partsupp.ps_partkey)
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
          inner join partsupp
          on (orders.o_orderkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
        on (orders.o_clerk <= orders.o_orderstatus)
      on (orders.o_orderkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
    inner join customer
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_mktsegment <= customer.c_mktsegment)
        inner join supplier
          inner join region
          on (supplier.s_comment = region.r_comment )
        on (customer.c_acctbal < customer.c_acctbal)
      inner join region
      on (region.r_name >= customer.c_phone)
    on (part.p_retailprice is NULL)
where orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate;
nl: What are the supply costs, available quantities, and part keys for each supplier that provides a specific part, along with the total account balance of the customers who have ordered this part, the region where they live, and the order date?

  nation.n_regionkey, 
  lineitem.l_shipmode, 
  nation.n_name,

    cast(cast(null as inet) as inet)),

  lineitem.l_extendedprice,

sql:
select  
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  region.r_name, 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as inet) as inet)), 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  region.r_name, 
  lineitem.l_receiptdate
from 
  supplier
        inner join lineitem
        on (supplier.s_acctbal >= lineitem.l_quantity)
      inner join customer
      on (lineitem.l_returnflag >= lineitem.l_shipmode)
    inner join nation
      inner join customer
          inner join orders
          on (customer.c_acctbal = customer.c_acctbal)
        inner join region
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_shippriority = region.r_regionkey)
          inner join region
          on (region.r_name < orders.o_clerk)
        on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
      on (nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey )
    on (customer.c_address is not NULL)
where region.r_regionkey is not NULL
limit 139;
nl: What are the nation, region, return flag, comment, and receipt date for each supplier that has a minimum account balance equal to or greater than the quantity of items returned, along with the clerk handling the order?

    inner join part
      inner join region
        inner join partsupp
        on (region.r_regionkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
      on (region.r_regionkey < partsupp.ps_suppkey)
    on (customer.c_comment = part.p_name )
where lineitem.l_partkey <= partsupp.ps_suppkey

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  nation.n_name, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as oid) as oid)), 
  lineitem.l_tax, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  supplier.s_name
from 
  orders
        inner join nation
          inner join orders
              inner join partsupp
                inner join partsupp
                on (partsupp.ps_availqty < partsupp.ps_suppkey)
              on (orders.o_clerk < orders.o_clerk)
            inner join supplier
            on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
          on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
        on (orders.o_totalprice = orders.o_totalprice)
      inner join part
        inner join nation
        on (part.p_brand > part.p_container)
      on (orders.o_clerk = part.p_mfgr )
    inner join nation
            inner join nation
              inner join orders
                  inner join orders
                  on (orders.o_totalprice > orders.o_totalprice)
                inner join lineitem
                on (lineitem.l_linestatus = orders.o_orderstatus)
              on (nation.n_regionkey = orders.o_shippriority)
            on (lineitem.l_discount = lineitem.l_discount)
          inner join partsupp
            inner join nation
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (orders.o_clerk = orders.o_orderpriority)
        inner join orders
        on (lineitem.l_shipdate = orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join orders
      on (nation.n_name = orders.o_orderstatus )
    on (part.p_mfgr = orders.o_orderstatus )
where partsupp.ps_supplycost is NULL
limit 111;
nl: What are the names of suppliers who have supplied products with a discount, and what is their region?

  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  lineitem.l_commitdate
from 
  customer
    inner join lineitem
        inner join region
        on (lineitem.l_returnflag = region.r_name )
      inner join region
      on (lineitem.l_returnflag >= lineitem.l_linestatus)
    on (customer.c_comment = region.r_comment )
where region.r_name is not NULL
limit 103;
nl: What are the names of regions, market segments, and commit dates for customers who have made a purchase in each region?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as xid8) as xid8)), 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2))
from 
  supplier
      inner join partsupp
      on (supplier.s_acctbal = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    inner join region
          inner join supplier
          on (region.r_name = supplier.s_name )
        inner join part
            inner join lineitem
            on (lineitem.l_linestatus > part.p_brand)
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_shipdate)
        on (lineitem.l_shipdate >= lineitem.l_shipdate)
      inner join supplier
              inner join region
              on (supplier.s_comment = region.r_comment )
            inner join supplier
            on (region.r_comment = supplier.s_address )
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join lineitem
            inner join partsupp
            on (partsupp.ps_availqty > lineitem.l_orderkey)
          inner join nation
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (region.r_regionkey = nation.n_nationkey )
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate >= lineitem.l_commitdate)
    on (supplier.s_comment = region.r_comment )
where nation.n_nationkey is NULL
limit 162;
nl: What are the supplier nation keys, along with any minimum and total values, for suppliers that have no comment?

nl: What are the order key, customer key, clerk, average total price, comment, and other details for each order where the clerk is greater than themselves, along with some additional information?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_comment, 
  customer.c_mktsegment
from 
  region
    inner join partsupp
      inner join nation
        inner join orders
            inner join customer
            on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
          inner join customer
          on (orders.o_clerk > orders.o_orderpriority)
        on (nation.n_name = orders.o_orderstatus )
      on (nation.n_name < customer.c_mktsegment)
    on (orders.o_clerk is NULL)
where nation.n_comment is NULL;

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost
from 
  customer
      inner join supplier
          inner join customer
          on (supplier.s_name > supplier.s_phone)
        inner join partsupp
              inner join lineitem
              on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = lineitem.l_quantity )
            inner join region
            on (lineitem.l_shipmode = region.r_name)
          inner join partsupp
          on (lineitem.l_quantity = lineitem.l_discount)
        on (lineitem.l_tax < lineitem.l_tax)
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate > lineitem.l_shipdate)
    inner join part
    on (lineitem.l_shipdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)
where lineitem.l_shipdate = lineitem.l_shipdate
limit 76;
nl: What are the part keys and supply costs of parts that have been shipped with a tax rate less than their original price, considering only orders where the shipment date is after the commitment date?

sql:
select  
  min(
    cast(orders.o_orderpriority as bpchar)), 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_comment, 
  nation.n_name, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  region.r_comment, 
  supplier.s_address, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  orders.o_shippriority, 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_name, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  max(
    cast(orders.o_orderdate as date)), 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  supplier.s_acctbal
from 
  supplier
        inner join region
        on (region.r_name > supplier.s_phone)
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join nation
    on (orders.o_orderstatus = orders.o_clerk)

        on (part.p_retailprice > supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join customer
          inner join nation
          on (customer.c_phone > customer.c_phone)
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_custkey > customer.c_nationkey)
      on (customer.c_phone >= part.p_mfgr)

where supplier.s_acctbal is NULL

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_linestatus
from 
  customer
            inner join lineitem
              inner join partsupp
              on (lineitem.l_shipdate = lineitem.l_commitdate)
            on (customer.c_acctbal >= lineitem.l_discount)
          inner join lineitem
          on (partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
        inner join orders
          inner join part
          on (orders.o_clerk = part.p_mfgr )
        on (lineitem.l_shipdate > lineitem.l_commitdate)
      inner join lineitem
        inner join supplier
          inner join nation
            inner join part
            on (nation.n_nationkey = part.p_partkey)
          on (nation.n_nationkey < supplier.s_nationkey)
        on (supplier.s_acctbal >= lineitem.l_tax)
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate < orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join nation
    on (orders.o_orderpriority = nation.n_name )
where lineitem.l_orderkey is not NULL;

from

        inner join region
          inner join customer
              inner join part
              on (customer.c_mktsegment >= part.p_brand)
            inner join supplier

            on (customer.c_acctbal < customer.c_acctbal)
          on (supplier.s_name = customer.c_mktsegment)
        on (lineitem.l_returnflag > lineitem.l_returnflag)
      inner join part

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_address, 
  region.r_name, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4)), 
  region.r_comment, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  max(
    cast(partsupp.ps_suppkey as int4)), 
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  customer.c_address, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  customer.c_name, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  supplier.s_name, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as money) as money)), 
  supplier.s_name, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  partsupp.ps_comment
from 
  customer
      inner join orders
        inner join partsupp
        on (orders.o_clerk > orders.o_clerk)
      on (partsupp.ps_suppkey >= orders.o_custkey)
    inner join supplier
        inner join region
          inner join supplier
            inner join region
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
            on (orders.o_clerk >= orders.o_clerk)
          on (supplier.s_acctbal > orders.o_totalprice)
        on (region.r_name = region.r_name)
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate )
    on (supplier.s_acctbal is NULL)
where orders.o_totalprice = partsupp.ps_supplycost;

limit 117;

    cast(partsupp.ps_supplycost as "numeric")), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  lineitem.l_tax, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey
from 
  lineitem
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_regionkey >= nation.n_regionkey)
      inner join partsupp
      on (lineitem.l_discount <= lineitem.l_discount)
    inner join nation
    on (lineitem.l_quantity > lineitem.l_tax)
where lineitem.l_receiptdate is not NULL;

      on (customer.c_acctbal <= part.p_retailprice)
    on (nation.n_name is not NULL)
where part.p_mfgr >= customer.c_mktsegment
limit 156;

sql:

  lineitem.l_extendedprice, 
  lineitem.l_shipmode, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as timestamptz) as timestamptz)), 
  nation.n_name, 
  sum(
    cast(orders.o_custkey as int4)), 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  lineitem.l_commitdate
from 
  lineitem
    inner join region
          inner join nation
          on (region.r_regionkey <= region.r_regionkey)
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_totalprice > orders.o_totalprice)
      inner join nation
      on (nation.n_name >= region.r_name)

where orders.o_comment is not NULL;

    on (lineitem.l_returnflag is NULL)

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost
from 
  lineitem
    inner join part
              inner join supplier
              on (supplier.s_acctbal >= part.p_retailprice)
            inner join supplier
            on (part.p_container < part.p_container)
          inner join partsupp
          on (supplier.s_suppkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
        inner join nation
        on (supplier.s_name < supplier.s_phone)
      inner join lineitem
            inner join lineitem
              inner join lineitem
              on (lineitem.l_linestatus >= lineitem.l_shipmode)
            on (lineitem.l_shipmode > lineitem.l_shipmode)
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_shipmode < lineitem.l_returnflag)
        inner join partsupp
        on (lineitem.l_partkey <= lineitem.l_suppkey)
      on (lineitem.l_shipmode <= part.p_mfgr)
    on (lineitem.l_returnflag = lineitem.l_returnflag)
where lineitem.l_extendedprice is NULL;

      inner join nation
          inner join lineitem

            on (lineitem.l_suppkey <= orders.o_shippriority)
          on (lineitem.l_partkey >= nation.n_regionkey)
        inner join customer
        on (lineitem.l_commitdate >= orders.o_orderdate)

from 
  supplier
where supplier.s_acctbal is not NULL
limit 14;
nl: What is the average account balance for each supplier, along with the total amount, nation key, and phone number?

sql:
select  
  part.p_partkey
from 
  part
where part.p_mfgr is NULL
limit 95;
nl: What are the part keys of all manufacturers with no manufacturer information?

sql:
select distinct 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  count(*)
from 
  supplier
      inner join region
      on (supplier.s_address = region.r_comment )
    inner join lineitem
      inner join lineitem
              inner join region
              on (lineitem.l_orderkey <= region.r_regionkey)
            inner join nation
            on (lineitem.l_shipdate = lineitem.l_receiptdate)
          inner join partsupp
          on (partsupp.ps_availqty >= partsupp.ps_partkey)
        inner join orders
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > lineitem.l_discount)
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate <= lineitem.l_commitdate)
    on (supplier.s_name is not NULL)
where lineitem.l_receiptdate <= lineitem.l_commitdate
limit 71;
nl: What are the unique nation keys and how many orders were made in each nation where the supplier's name is not null?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_phone, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  customer.c_name
from 
  customer
    inner join orders
    on (orders.o_orderpriority is NULL)
where orders.o_custkey < orders.o_custkey
limit 72;
nl: What are the phone numbers and names of customers who have no priority in their orders, along with how many such customers there are?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_address
from 
  supplier
where supplier.s_suppkey is NULL;
nl: What are the addresses of suppliers with no supplier key?

sql:
select  
  part.p_brand, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  part.p_name, 
  part.p_container, 
  part.p_brand, 
  part.p_size, 
  part.p_container, 
  part.p_comment, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  part.p_partkey
from 
  part
where part.p_container is NULL
limit 85;
nl: What are the details of products with no container, including brand, manufacturer, name, size, and retail price?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_extendedprice, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum))
from 
  lineitem
where lineitem.l_commitdate > lineitem.l_commitdate
limit 128;
nl: What is the extended price of each item, and what is the maximum value?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_suppkey
from 
  nation
    inner join supplier
    on (supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
where nation.n_name = supplier.s_phone
limit 174;
nl: What are the phone numbers of suppliers in a specific nation who have an account balance greater than another supplier's account balance?

sql:
select  
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")), 
  lineitem.l_quantity
from 
  lineitem
      inner join region
      on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct > region.r_name)
    inner join part
    on (lineitem.l_partkey is not NULL)
where lineitem.l_tax = lineitem.l_tax
limit 137;
nl: What are the minimum and quantity of items shipped from each region, considering only regions where a specific instruction was used?

sql:
select  
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  orders.o_orderkey
from 
  orders
where orders.o_custkey is not NULL
limit 108;
nl: What are the order status, total price, and key details of all non-null customer orders, along with the clerk responsible for each order?

sql:
select  
  orders.o_clerk, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")), 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  orders.o_totalprice
from 
  orders
where orders.o_orderkey is not NULL
limit 116;
nl: What are the details of all non-null orders, including the clerk, order key, customer key, and total price?

sql:
select  
  max(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as oid) as oid)), 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty
from 
  lineitem
            inner join supplier
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
            on (orders.o_custkey = orders.o_orderkey)
          inner join partsupp
            inner join orders
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join supplier
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (lineitem.l_tax = lineitem.l_quantity)
      inner join customer
      on (supplier.s_acctbal > orders.o_totalprice)
    inner join partsupp
    on (supplier.s_phone is not NULL)
where supplier.s_address is not NULL;
nl: What are the maximum values of null, along with the comments and available quantities for each part-supplier combination?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_comment
from 
  lineitem
where lineitem.l_suppkey is not NULL
limit 34;
nl: What are the comments for orders from suppliers that have provided something?

sql:
select  
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  orders.o_orderdate
from 
  orders
        inner join customer
          inner join orders
            inner join customer
            on (orders.o_totalprice = customer.c_acctbal )
          on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
        on (orders.o_shippriority <= customer.c_nationkey)
      inner join supplier
      on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join part
        inner join nation
        on (part.p_retailprice <= part.p_retailprice)
      inner join lineitem
          inner join supplier
          on (lineitem.l_partkey < lineitem.l_partkey)
        inner join region
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_nationkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
        on (lineitem.l_orderkey >= supplier.s_nationkey)
      on (supplier.s_acctbal >= lineitem.l_quantity)
    on (supplier.s_nationkey is NULL)
where part.p_brand is not NULL;
nl: What orders were placed by customers with outstanding balances, where the order date is after the payment date, and the supplier's nation key matches the region's nation key?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_name, 
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as anyarray) as anyarray)), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as tid) as tid)), 
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  customer.c_name, 
  min(
    cast(customer.c_custkey as int4)), 
  customer.c_comment, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  customer.c_comment, 
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "time") as "time")), 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  customer.c_phone
from 
  customer
where customer.c_acctbal < customer.c_acctbal
limit 57;
nl: What are the names, account balances, and other details of customers who have a certain balance, along with their market segment, phone number, and nation key?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_address, 
  part.p_type, 
  max(
    cast(region.r_name as bpchar)), 
  customer.c_phone, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  orders.o_comment
from 
  supplier
      inner join region
      on (supplier.s_name = region.r_name )
    inner join supplier
          inner join customer
            inner join region
            on (customer.c_phone <= customer.c_phone)
          on (customer.c_phone < customer.c_phone)
        inner join part
        on (region.r_name < supplier.s_phone)
      inner join orders
      on (region.r_name = orders.o_orderstatus )
    on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal )
where supplier.s_acctbal < orders.o_totalprice;
nl: What are the addresses of suppliers, types of parts, most common region names, phone numbers and nation keys of customers, and order comments for all orders where the total price is less than the account balance?

sql:
select  
  min(
    cast(orders.o_orderdate as date)), 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as "time") as "time")), 
  supplier.s_address, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  lineitem.l_receiptdate
from 
  partsupp
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey)
      inner join orders
      on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    inner join supplier
        inner join lineitem
        on (supplier.s_suppkey = supplier.s_nationkey)
      inner join supplier
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate = orders.o_orderdate)
    on (supplier.s_address is not NULL)
where orders.o_orderpriority is NULL
limit 79;
nl: What are the earliest and latest dates, along with supplier addresses and keys, and receipt dates for all orders that have no priority?

sql:
select  
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  orders.o_comment, 
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct, 
  count(*)
from 
  lineitem
    inner join orders
      inner join part
      on (orders.o_totalprice < orders.o_totalprice)
    on (orders.o_custkey > lineitem.l_orderkey)
where part.p_type is not NULL
limit 113;
nl: What are the order priorities, minimum shipping instructions, comments, and counts of orders where the customer key is higher than the order key, the total price is less than itself, and the part type exists?

sql:
select  
  min(
    cast(lineitem.l_shipinstruct as bpchar))
from 
  lineitem
where lineitem.l_suppkey is NULL
limit 80;
nl: What are the earliest shipping instructions for suppliers with no key?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_tax, 
  lineitem.l_tax, 
  lineitem.l_comment, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4)), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  sum(
    cast(lineitem.l_quantity as "numeric")), 
  lineitem.l_shipmode, 
  lineitem.l_commitdate, 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  lineitem.l_orderkey, 
  lineitem.l_orderkey
from 
  lineitem
where lineitem.l_shipdate < lineitem.l_commitdate
limit 13;

sql:
select  
  orders.o_clerk
from 
  orders
        inner join part
        on (orders.o_orderstatus = part.p_mfgr )
      inner join supplier
      on (orders.o_totalprice > supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join partsupp
      inner join part
      on (part.p_mfgr >= part.p_container)
    on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice )
where partsupp.ps_comment is not NULL
limit 90;

sql:

  customer.c_custkey, 
  customer.c_address
from 
  customer
where customer.c_comment is not NULL;

sql:
select

from 
  partsupp
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_clerk <= orders.o_orderpriority)
      inner join customer
      on (customer.c_acctbal >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)

    on (customer.c_address is NULL)
where orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate
limit 90;

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as money) as money))
from 
  supplier
    inner join partsupp
    on (supplier.s_name < supplier.s_phone)
where supplier.s_suppkey >= partsupp.ps_availqty
limit 142;
nl: What are the part keys and supplier keys for suppliers who have a certain number of available parts, along with how many total parts they have?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  part.p_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  nation.n_nationkey
from 
  nation
        inner join partsupp
        on (nation.n_name < nation.n_name)
      inner join nation
        inner join part
        on (nation.n_name = part.p_mfgr )
      on (part.p_container <= part.p_mfgr)
    inner join region
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_phone <= supplier.s_phone)
      inner join region
        inner join part
        on (region.r_comment = part.p_name )
      on (part.p_retailprice >= supplier.s_acctbal)
    on (part.p_mfgr is not NULL)
where supplier.s_suppkey < nation.n_regionkey
limit 79;

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  avg(
    cast(supplier.s_suppkey as int4)), 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)), 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8))

  supplier
where supplier.s_suppkey is not NULL
limit 12;

sql:

  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  partsupp.ps_comment
from 
  partsupp
where partsupp.ps_supplycost is not NULL;
nl: What is the sum of null values, along with comments, available quantities, and supply costs for all suppliers?

sql:
select  
  part.p_type, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  part.p_name, 
  region.r_comment, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  region.r_name, 
  nation.n_name
from 
  orders
    inner join region
        inner join part
        on (part.p_retailprice > part.p_retailprice)
      inner join nation
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey )
      on (part.p_partkey = region.r_regionkey)

where orders.o_orderstatus <= nation.n_name

sql:
select  
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  nation.n_name, 
  nation.n_nationkey
from 
  nation
where nation.n_nationkey is not NULL
limit 122;
nl: What are the details of each region, including its name and comment, for all nations that exist?

sql:
select  
  part.p_size, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  max(
    cast(part.p_size as int4)), 
  part.p_size, 
  sum(
    cast(part.p_partkey as int4)), 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4)),

from 
  part
where part.p_container = part.p_brand
limit 139;

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_address, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  supplier.s_name
from 
  supplier
    inner join orders
    on (orders.o_orderpriority is not NULL)
where orders.o_shippriority is not NULL;
nl: What are the address, account balance, and name of suppliers who have shipped orders with a priority?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_name, 
  supplier.s_acctbal
from 
  supplier
    inner join lineitem
    on (supplier.s_nationkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
where lineitem.l_extendedprice is not NULL;
nl: What are the names and account balances of suppliers that have placed orders with non-null extended prices?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_extendedprice, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost
from 
  lineitem
      inner join part
        inner join partsupp
        on (part.p_mfgr > part.p_container)
      on (partsupp.ps_availqty = part.p_size)
    inner join partsupp
    on (partsupp.ps_supplycost is NULL)
where lineitem.l_returnflag is not NULL
limit 86;
nl: What are the extended prices, available quantities, part keys, supply costs of products with no returns, where manufacturers produce more than container sizes and supply costs are unknown?

sql:
select  
  max(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_comment, 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_comment, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_name, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  avg(
    cast(region.r_regionkey as int4)), 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  min(
    cast(region.r_name as bpchar)), 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_comment, 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_name, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_comment
from 
  region
where region.r_regionkey is NULL
limit 121;
nl: What are the maximum and minimum values in the region table, along with the average region key, for regions without a specified region key?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_shipmode
from 
  nation
    inner join lineitem
        inner join partsupp
        on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct < lineitem.l_returnflag)
      inner join lineitem
        inner join orders
        on (lineitem.l_discount > lineitem.l_quantity)
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_receiptdate)
    on (lineitem.l_shipdate is not NULL)
where partsupp.ps_partkey is NULL
limit 110;
nl: What shipping modes are used for orders with no part supplies?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  max(
    cast(lineitem.l_quantity as "numeric"))
from 
  lineitem
          inner join region
            inner join orders
              inner join partsupp
              on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
            on (orders.o_custkey <= partsupp.ps_partkey)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = lineitem.l_quantity)
        inner join supplier
        on (orders.o_comment = supplier.s_address )
      inner join nation
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_partkey <= lineitem.l_linenumber)
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_commitdate)
    inner join orders
    on (supplier.s_nationkey is NULL)
where orders.o_totalprice is not NULL
limit 107;
nl: What is the maximum quantity of each part that a supplier has ordered, along with their account balance?

sql:
select  
  orders.o_clerk, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  max(
    cast(orders.o_orderdate as date)), 
  orders.o_orderpriority
from 
  orders
where orders.o_orderpriority is not NULL
limit 72;
nl: What are the details of each order, including the clerk, total price, order date, and status, along with the maximum order date and priority, for the first 72 orders that have a specified priority?

sql:
select  
  part.p_partkey
from 
  orders
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      inner join partsupp
      on (partsupp.ps_partkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
    inner join part
    on (part.p_size is not NULL)
where orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate
limit 104;
nl: What are the part keys of all parts that have a supply cost equal to their available quantity and were ordered before their order date?

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  region.r_comment, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as date) as date))
from 
  partsupp
    inner join region
      inner join customer
      on (region.r_regionkey >= customer.c_nationkey)
    on (partsupp.ps_partkey is not NULL)
where customer.c_comment is NULL
limit 72;
nl: What are the supplier keys, nation keys, phone numbers, and region comments for suppliers who don't have any comments about their customers, along with a minimum value?

sql:
select  
  max(
    cast(cast(null as inet) as inet)), 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")), 
  region.r_comment
from 
  region
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join region
      inner join partsupp
      on (partsupp.ps_availqty <= region.r_regionkey)
    on (region.r_comment = partsupp.ps_comment )
where orders.o_totalprice is NULL;
nl: What are the maximum and minimum dates, order status, and comments for regions where available quantities match comments?

sql:
select  
  region.r_comment, 
  orders.o_orderpriority
from 
  partsupp
        inner join part
          inner join orders
          on (part.p_container = orders.o_orderstatus)
        on (part.p_size >= partsupp.ps_availqty)
      inner join customer
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_acctbal <= customer.c_acctbal)
        inner join region
        on (customer.c_phone = region.r_name )
      on (partsupp.ps_suppkey < customer.c_nationkey)
    inner join lineitem
    on (customer.c_name is NULL)
where orders.o_shippriority is not NULL
limit 102;
nl: What are the comments and order priorities for regions where customers have a certain balance, phone number matches a region name, and there's no customer name?

sql:
select  
  region.r_comment, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  region.r_comment
from 
  region
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_acctbal >= customer.c_acctbal)
      inner join supplier
      on (region.r_regionkey = region.r_regionkey)
    inner join nation
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_name > nation.n_name)
      inner join customer
      on (nation.n_regionkey > nation.n_regionkey)
    on (nation.n_nationkey is NULL)
where nation.n_comment is not NULL;
nl: What are the comments for regions and suppliers, along with any region-specific information?

sql:
select  
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  partsupp.ps_comment
from 
  partsupp
      inner join part
        inner join nation
          inner join supplier
          on (nation.n_nationkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
        on (part.p_container >= part.p_container)
      on (partsupp.ps_availqty = nation.n_nationkey )
    inner join part
    on (part.p_container is not NULL)
where partsupp.ps_availqty < nation.n_regionkey
limit 115;
nl: What are the region keys, supplier IDs, and comments for suppliers in each region that have available quantities less than their corresponding region key?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_linenumber, 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  supplier.s_address
from 
  region
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join supplier
        on (orders.o_shippriority = supplier.s_suppkey )
      inner join nation
      on (orders.o_orderkey < orders.o_shippriority)
    inner join lineitem
    on (region.r_regionkey is not NULL)
where lineitem.l_commitdate is NULL
limit 170;
nl: What are the order numbers, return flags, customer keys, priority levels, and supplier addresses for all uncommitted orders in a specific region?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_name
from 
  customer
where customer.c_nationkey is NULL
limit 156;
nl: What are the names of customers who have no nation key?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_suppkey, 
  lineitem.l_shipdate
from 
  lineitem
      inner join customer
      on (customer.c_nationkey < customer.c_nationkey)
    inner join partsupp
    on (lineitem.l_commitdate is NULL)
where lineitem.l_commitdate < lineitem.l_shipdate

  customer.c_custkey, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  min(
    cast(orders.o_shippriority as int4)), 
  part.p_type, 
  customer.c_name, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  customer.c_comment,

  orders.o_comment, 
  part.p_type, 
  part.p_size, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  region.r_name
from 
  region
        inner join supplier
        on (region.r_regionkey >= supplier.s_suppkey)
      inner join customer
          inner join orders
          on (customer.c_custkey = orders.o_orderkey )
        inner join supplier
          inner join part
          on (supplier.s_suppkey = part.p_partkey )
        on (supplier.s_acctbal = customer.c_acctbal)
      on (supplier.s_suppkey < region.r_regionkey)
    inner join partsupp
    on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)

sql:
select  
  part.p_partkey, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  count(*), 
  lineitem.l_commitdate, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)), 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey
from 
  lineitem
            inner join part
            on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct >= lineitem.l_linestatus)
          inner join part
          on (lineitem.l_orderkey < lineitem.l_suppkey)
        inner join nation
        on (lineitem.l_discount <= part.p_retailprice)
      inner join nation
          inner join part
              inner join part
              on (part.p_partkey = part.p_partkey )
            inner join customer
              inner join region
              on (customer.c_nationkey > region.r_regionkey)
            on (customer.c_nationkey < part.p_size)
          on (part.p_retailprice > part.p_retailprice)
        inner join lineitem
        on (part.p_retailprice = lineitem.l_quantity )
      on (lineitem.l_shipdate < lineitem.l_receiptdate)
    inner join partsupp
      inner join part
      on (part.p_brand < part.p_mfgr)
    on (part.p_mfgr is not NULL)
where lineitem.l_commitdate is NULL;

            inner join customer
            on (orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey )
          inner join part
          on (orders.o_custkey >= orders.o_orderkey)
        on (region.r_name > part.p_brand)
      inner join lineitem

select

    cast(cast(null as tid) as tid)), 
  part.p_type,

  nation.n_comment
from 
  lineitem
        inner join orders
        on (lineitem.l_quantity = orders.o_totalprice )
      inner join lineitem
        inner join lineitem
          inner join supplier
            inner join nation
            on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (lineitem.l_discount = supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (lineitem.l_quantity >= lineitem.l_tax)
      on (nation.n_regionkey < lineitem.l_linenumber)
    inner join nation
        inner join partsupp
            inner join lineitem
            on (partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
          inner join nation
          on (lineitem.l_orderkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
        on (lineitem.l_commitdate < lineitem.l_shipdate)
      inner join part
        inner join nation
          inner join partsupp
            inner join nation
              inner join nation
              on (nation.n_regionkey = nation.n_nationkey )
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (part.p_brand <= part.p_brand)
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)

sql:
select  
  part.p_mfgr
from 
  partsupp
      inner join lineitem
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
          inner join customer
          on (lineitem.l_shipdate = lineitem.l_shipdate)
        inner join partsupp
          inner join part
            inner join region
            on (part.p_retailprice > part.p_retailprice)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < part.p_retailprice)
        on (lineitem.l_orderkey >= supplier.s_nationkey)
      on (part.p_retailprice <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    inner join supplier
          inner join nation
          on (nation.n_name <= supplier.s_name)
        inner join part
        on (nation.n_nationkey = part.p_partkey )
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
    on (orders.o_orderstatus is not NULL)
where lineitem.l_receiptdate >= lineitem.l_commitdate;

select  
  orders.o_shippriority, 
  part.p_comment
from 
  orders
        inner join supplier
        on (orders.o_clerk = supplier.s_name )
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join part
              inner join partsupp
                inner join part
                on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= partsupp.ps_suppkey)
              on (part.p_partkey < part.p_size)
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
          inner join orders
          on (part.p_size <= orders.o_orderkey)
        inner join part
          inner join lineitem
            inner join orders
              inner join customer
              on (orders.o_orderpriority < orders.o_orderstatus)
            on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)
          on (part.p_size < part.p_size)
        on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join nation
      on (orders.o_orderstatus = nation.n_name )
    on (orders.o_orderpriority is not NULL)
where customer.c_mktsegment is not NULL;

select distinct

  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  part.p_brand,

  nation.n_nationkey, 
  part.p_comment, 
  nation.n_regionkey
from 
  lineitem
      inner join part
        inner join nation
        on (part.p_brand = nation.n_name )
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate = lineitem.l_receiptdate)
    inner join lineitem
      inner join supplier
            inner join part
            on (supplier.s_name = part.p_mfgr )
          inner join supplier
            inner join region
              inner join part
              on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
            on (supplier.s_phone < supplier.s_name)
          on (part.p_container = part.p_mfgr)
        inner join nation
          inner join supplier
          on (nation.n_regionkey >= supplier.s_nationkey)
        on (supplier.s_suppkey > supplier.s_nationkey)
      on (part.p_container <= supplier.s_name)
    on (lineitem.l_tax = lineitem.l_discount)
where region.r_comment is NULL

from 
  lineitem
    inner join supplier
      inner join lineitem
        inner join region
          inner join nation
              inner join part
              on (nation.n_nationkey > nation.n_nationkey)

sql:
select  
  max(
    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")), 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as text) as text)), 
  lineitem.l_extendedprice, 
  orders.o_shippriority, 
  region.r_comment, 
  region.r_comment, 
  region.r_comment, 
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct
from 
  orders
        inner join customer
        on (orders.o_shippriority >= customer.c_custkey)
      inner join orders
        inner join orders
          inner join orders
            inner join lineitem
            on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
          on (lineitem.l_commitdate > orders.o_orderdate)
        on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate )
      on (customer.c_nationkey = lineitem.l_suppkey)
    inner join region
        inner join orders
            inner join region
              inner join orders
              on (region.r_name >= orders.o_orderpriority)
            on (region.r_name < region.r_name)
          inner join nation
            inner join partsupp
            on (nation.n_regionkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
          on (region.r_name >= region.r_name)
        on (region.r_name < orders.o_orderpriority)
      inner join lineitem
        inner join region
        on (lineitem.l_shipmode > lineitem.l_returnflag)
      on (nation.n_regionkey <= orders.o_orderkey)
    on (lineitem.l_shipdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
where customer.c_acctbal is not NULL

sql:
select  
  max(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4)), 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  region.r_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct,

  partsupp.ps_availqty,

    cast(cast(null as anyarray) as anyarray)), 
  partsupp.ps_partkey
from

    inner join lineitem
              inner join partsupp
              on (lineitem.l_discount = lineitem.l_tax)
            inner join customer
              inner join supplier
              on (customer.c_custkey = supplier.s_suppkey)
            on (partsupp.ps_comment = customer.c_name )
          inner join nation
            inner join orders

        inner join part

            on (part.p_container = supplier.s_name)
          inner join part

where orders.o_orderkey < orders.o_orderkey;

sql:
select distinct 
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey
from 
  customer
        inner join customer
          inner join partsupp
              inner join supplier
              on (partsupp.ps_availqty = supplier.s_suppkey )
            inner join region
            on (supplier.s_name >= supplier.s_name)
          on (customer.c_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (customer.c_mktsegment >= customer.c_mktsegment)
      inner join nation
        inner join supplier
        on (nation.n_nationkey >= nation.n_nationkey)
      on (supplier.s_name < customer.c_phone)
    inner join lineitem
      inner join nation
              inner join orders
                inner join partsupp
                on (orders.o_comment = partsupp.ps_comment )
              on (orders.o_orderstatus >= orders.o_clerk)
            inner join region
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = orders.o_totalprice)
          inner join orders
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = orders.o_totalprice )
        inner join part
        on (orders.o_custkey < region.r_regionkey)
      on (lineitem.l_quantity > orders.o_totalprice)
    on (orders.o_custkey is not NULL)
where partsupp.ps_availqty is not NULL
limit 25;

    cast(lineitem.l_commitdate as date)), 
  lineitem.l_linestatus, 
  sum(
    cast(orders.o_custkey as int4)), 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)), 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  part.p_comment, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  lineitem.l_partkey, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  lineitem.l_receiptdate, 
  region.r_name, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey
from 
  partsupp
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
        inner join part
        on (partsupp.ps_partkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
      inner join partsupp
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join partsupp
            inner join part
            on (part.p_size >= part.p_size)
          inner join region
          on (part.p_retailprice >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (lineitem.l_extendedprice > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate >= lineitem.l_receiptdate)
    inner join partsupp
          inner join nation
          on (nation.n_name < nation.n_name)
        inner join region
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_mktsegment = customer.c_phone)
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_linenumber > lineitem.l_linenumber)
        on (lineitem.l_commitdate > lineitem.l_commitdate)
      inner join orders
      on (nation.n_name > lineitem.l_shipmode)
    on (partsupp.ps_availqty is not NULL)
where part.p_mfgr is not NULL

              inner join nation
              on (nation.n_name >= nation.n_name)
            on (orders.o_custkey = region.r_regionkey )
          inner join customer
          on (nation.n_comment = customer.c_name )
        inner join region
        on (customer.c_acctbal < customer.c_acctbal)
      inner join supplier
      on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join partsupp
        inner join nation
          inner join customer
          on (nation.n_regionkey >= nation.n_regionkey)
        on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
      inner join partsupp
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_shipdate)
      on (customer.c_mktsegment > lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
    on (region.r_name is NULL)
where lineitem.l_shipinstruct < customer.c_mktsegment;
nl: What are the names and comments of regions where customers have a higher account balance than their previous balance, and what instructions did they give for shipping?

from

where part.p_container is not NULL
limit 91;

sql:

from

        inner join orders
          inner join nation
          on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
        on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join nation
          inner join part
          on (nation.n_regionkey = part.p_partkey )
        inner join nation
        on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
      on (orders.o_orderstatus = part.p_mfgr )
    inner join nation
    on (nation.n_comment is NULL)
where orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate
limit 94;

sql:
select  
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as inet) as inet)), 
  part.p_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  lineitem.l_suppkey, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  nation.n_name
from 
  partsupp
          inner join lineitem
            inner join region
              inner join part
                inner join nation
                  inner join partsupp
                  on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
                on (part.p_mfgr > part.p_container)
              on (part.p_container < part.p_brand)
            on (region.r_name = lineitem.l_shipmode)
          on (lineitem.l_orderkey < partsupp.ps_suppkey)
        inner join orders
        on (lineitem.l_shipdate <= lineitem.l_commitdate)
      inner join partsupp
      on (lineitem.l_quantity < part.p_retailprice)
    inner join supplier
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
          inner join region
          on (supplier.s_nationkey > orders.o_shippriority)
        inner join supplier
            inner join region
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
            on (supplier.s_acctbal < orders.o_totalprice)
          inner join nation
              inner join region
                inner join lineitem
                on (lineitem.l_returnflag < lineitem.l_returnflag)
              on (nation.n_name < lineitem.l_returnflag)
            inner join partsupp
            on (nation.n_name >= nation.n_name)
          on (orders.o_orderpriority = region.r_name )
        on (supplier.s_comment = region.r_comment )
      inner join supplier
            inner join supplier
                inner join nation
                on (supplier.s_comment = nation.n_comment )
              inner join region
              on (region.r_regionkey <= region.r_regionkey)
            on (supplier.s_suppkey = nation.n_nationkey )
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_name > supplier.s_name)
        inner join supplier
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_phone = supplier.s_name)
        on (supplier.s_acctbal >= supplier.s_acctbal)
      on (orders.o_custkey >= lineitem.l_orderkey)
    on (nation.n_nationkey is not NULL)
where supplier.s_comment is not NULL;

sql:

          on (customer.c_acctbal = customer.c_acctbal )
        on (part.p_container = region.r_name)

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_partkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as oid) as oid))
from 
  region
      inner join supplier
      on (region.r_name >= supplier.s_phone)
    inner join customer
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_regionkey < customer.c_nationkey)
      inner join nation
              inner join part
              on (part.p_partkey >= part.p_size)
            inner join lineitem
              inner join supplier
                inner join lineitem
                on (lineitem.l_tax > lineitem.l_discount)
              on (lineitem.l_commitdate < lineitem.l_receiptdate)
            on (nation.n_name = lineitem.l_returnflag )
          inner join orders
            inner join orders
              inner join lineitem
              on (lineitem.l_discount = lineitem.l_discount)
            on (orders.o_shippriority < orders.o_custkey)
          on (nation.n_regionkey = orders.o_orderkey )
        inner join partsupp
              inner join part
              on (partsupp.ps_availqty >= partsupp.ps_partkey)
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
          inner join part
          on (part.p_retailprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
        on (lineitem.l_commitdate < orders.o_orderdate)
      on (orders.o_orderdate <= lineitem.l_shipdate)
    on (orders.o_clerk < orders.o_orderstatus)
where region.r_regionkey is NULL;
nl: What are the part keys, region keys, retail prices, and a minimum value for all lines where there is no region key?

sql:
select  
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey
from 
  region
          inner join supplier
              inner join partsupp
              on (supplier.s_name < supplier.s_name)
            inner join region
            on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join part
          inner join orders
          on (part.p_retailprice <= part.p_retailprice)
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = region.r_regionkey)
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join partsupp
    on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
where partsupp.ps_partkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey
limit 51;

sql:
select  
  part.p_container, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  part.p_retailprice
from 
  partsupp
      inner join orders
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_totalprice <= orders.o_totalprice)
      on (orders.o_custkey >= orders.o_orderkey)
    inner join part
        inner join lineitem
          inner join partsupp
            inner join orders
              inner join customer
                  inner join region
                  on (customer.c_acctbal < customer.c_acctbal)
                inner join nation
                on (customer.c_nationkey < nation.n_regionkey)
              on (orders.o_custkey <= nation.n_regionkey)
            on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
          on (lineitem.l_returnflag = customer.c_phone )
        on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join part
      on (nation.n_comment = part.p_name )
    on (orders.o_clerk is NULL)
where part.p_name is not NULL
limit 29;

      inner join nation
          inner join part
          on (part.p_container < part.p_brand)
        inner join partsupp
        on (nation.n_nationkey = partsupp.ps_partkey)
      on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= orders.o_orderkey)
    inner join nation
      inner join region
      on (nation.n_nationkey >= region.r_regionkey)
    on (region.r_regionkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
where orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate

sql:

sql:
select  
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  count(*), 
  nation.n_comment, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  region.r_comment, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz)), 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  customer.c_custkey
from 
  supplier
      inner join partsupp
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_phone <= supplier.s_phone)
          inner join region
            inner join region
            on (region.r_regionkey > region.r_regionkey)
          on (region.r_name = region.r_name)
        inner join nation
        on (region.r_name > region.r_name)
      on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join supplier
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_nationkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
          inner join partsupp
          on (supplier.s_suppkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty = partsupp.ps_partkey )
      inner join region
          inner join nation
          on (region.r_comment = nation.n_comment )
        inner join orders
          inner join customer
            inner join nation
            on (nation.n_regionkey > customer.c_nationkey)
          on (customer.c_acctbal < orders.o_totalprice)
        on (orders.o_totalprice = orders.o_totalprice)
      on (customer.c_address = region.r_comment )
    on (nation.n_comment is not NULL)
where supplier.s_comment is NULL
limit 178;
nl: What are the market segments, available quantities, and counts of customers who have no comment in their nation, along with their phone numbers, order statuses, and regions?

sql:
select  
  region.r_regionkey, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  max(
    cast(lineitem.l_returnflag as bpchar)), 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  partsupp.ps_comment
from 
  lineitem
      inner join supplier
        inner join customer
          inner join partsupp
            inner join lineitem
              inner join customer
                  inner join supplier
                  on (customer.c_mktsegment >= customer.c_phone)
                inner join customer
                on (customer.c_acctbal = customer.c_acctbal )
              on (customer.c_custkey < customer.c_nationkey)
            on (lineitem.l_shipdate >= lineitem.l_commitdate)
          on (lineitem.l_shipmode <= lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
        on (lineitem.l_returnflag > supplier.s_name)
      on (lineitem.l_discount <= lineitem.l_tax)
    inner join region
    on (customer.c_mktsegment <= lineitem.l_linestatus)
where lineitem.l_linenumber is NULL;
nl: What are the details of all orders that have no specific line number, including the region, supplier, customer market segment, and any relevant comments?

sql:

nl: What are the sizes, containers, types, manufacturers, and prices of all parts that have a higher retail price than their own retail price?

sql:
select  
  region.r_name, 
  nation.n_comment
from 
  region
        inner join region
          inner join customer
            inner join supplier
            on (customer.c_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (customer.c_custkey >= supplier.s_suppkey)
        on (customer.c_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join region
      on (region.r_regionkey = region.r_regionkey )
    inner join customer
        inner join orders
        on (customer.c_acctbal < orders.o_totalprice)
      inner join partsupp
          inner join supplier
              inner join orders
                inner join nation
                on (orders.o_comment = nation.n_comment )
              on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
            inner join lineitem
              inner join nation
              on (lineitem.l_quantity > lineitem.l_quantity)
            on (orders.o_comment = nation.n_comment )
          on (orders.o_custkey <= lineitem.l_orderkey)
        inner join nation
          inner join lineitem
              inner join region
                inner join customer
                on (customer.c_acctbal >= customer.c_acctbal)
              on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_shipdate)
            inner join orders
            on (lineitem.l_linestatus = orders.o_orderstatus )
          on (orders.o_totalprice >= lineitem.l_discount)
        on (orders.o_shippriority >= region.r_regionkey)
      on (lineitem.l_returnflag > orders.o_orderpriority)
    on (partsupp.ps_comment is NULL)
where customer.c_mktsegment = customer.c_mktsegment;
nl: What are the names of regions and comments from nations where customers have a higher account balance than suppliers, and how many such records exist?

sql:

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as money) as money)), 
  supplier.s_address, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  supplier.s_name
from 
  partsupp
          inner join orders
          on (partsupp.ps_comment = orders.o_comment )

              on (supplier.s_suppkey = supplier.s_nationkey)

          on (supplier.s_address = supplier.s_address )
        inner join region

      inner join partsupp

        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = nation.n_regionkey)

    on (lineitem.l_commitdate >= lineitem.l_receiptdate)

    cast(cast(null as tid) as tid))
from

    inner join part
        inner join lineitem
          inner join partsupp
          on (lineitem.l_tax = partsupp.ps_supplycost )
        on (part.p_brand = part.p_mfgr)
      inner join orders
          inner join part
            inner join partsupp
              inner join region
                  inner join part
                  on (part.p_brand > part.p_container)
                inner join orders
                on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
              on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
            on (part.p_retailprice <= orders.o_totalprice)
          on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join region
          inner join supplier
          on (region.r_name = supplier.s_name )
        on (orders.o_orderstatus = region.r_name )
      on (supplier.s_nationkey < part.p_partkey)
    on (part.p_mfgr = orders.o_orderstatus )
where part.p_brand is not NULL

select

  supplier.s_phone, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  orders.o_orderpriority,

    cast(cast(null as "time") as "time")), 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_comment
from 
  nation
              inner join region
              on (region.r_regionkey >= region.r_regionkey)
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_acctbal < customer.c_acctbal)
          inner join part
          on (region.r_regionkey = part.p_partkey )
        inner join nation
        on (part.p_name = nation.n_comment )
      inner join nation
          inner join nation
          on (nation.n_regionkey < nation.n_nationkey)
        inner join region
        on (nation.n_regionkey <= nation.n_nationkey)
      on (part.p_retailprice < customer.c_acctbal)
    inner join partsupp
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty = partsupp.ps_partkey )
      inner join lineitem
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_nationkey > lineitem.l_linenumber)
        inner join orders
              inner join supplier
              on (orders.o_totalprice < orders.o_totalprice)
            inner join nation
            on (orders.o_orderkey > orders.o_shippriority)
          inner join customer
          on (supplier.s_comment = customer.c_name )
        on (lineitem.l_suppkey < lineitem.l_orderkey)
      on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
    on (part.p_comment is not NULL)
where partsupp.ps_availqty < part.p_size
limit 77;

      inner join region
          inner join orders
              inner join nation
              on (orders.o_custkey = orders.o_orderkey)
            inner join nation

          on (region.r_regionkey = orders.o_orderkey )

select

from

            inner join supplier

          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_nationkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
        inner join region
        on (supplier.s_acctbal <= lineitem.l_discount)
      inner join nation
          inner join part
          on (part.p_retailprice <= part.p_retailprice)
        inner join region
              inner join part
              on (region.r_regionkey = part.p_size)
            inner join orders
              inner join customer
              on (customer.c_acctbal = customer.c_acctbal)
            on (orders.o_orderkey >= customer.c_custkey)
          inner join orders
          on (customer.c_acctbal > part.p_retailprice)
        on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
      on (supplier.s_name >= part.p_container)
    inner join part
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_acctbal < part.p_retailprice)
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join customer
        on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join lineitem
        inner join customer
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_suppkey > customer.c_custkey)
          inner join partsupp
          on (partsupp.ps_availqty < partsupp.ps_availqty)
        on (customer.c_custkey < lineitem.l_linenumber)
      on (customer.c_custkey = customer.c_custkey )

from

      inner join region
      on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
    inner join part
            inner join part
            on (part.p_brand < part.p_brand)
          inner join partsupp
          on (part.p_container >= part.p_mfgr)
        inner join nation
          inner join orders
          on (nation.n_name = orders.o_orderstatus )
        on (part.p_brand = orders.o_orderstatus )
      inner join region

        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
      on (part.p_retailprice < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
where region.r_regionkey is NULL;

select

    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn))
from 
  partsupp
        inner join nation
              inner join orders
                inner join region
                on (orders.o_custkey = region.r_regionkey )
              on (region.r_name > nation.n_name)
            inner join nation
            on (region.r_comment = nation.n_comment )
          inner join orders
          on (nation.n_comment = orders.o_comment )
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = orders.o_orderkey )
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderstatus < orders.o_orderpriority)
    inner join lineitem
          inner join customer
          on (lineitem.l_shipdate > lineitem.l_shipdate)
        inner join region
            inner join supplier
            on (region.r_name = supplier.s_name )
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
        on (orders.o_orderdate = lineitem.l_shipdate)
      inner join orders
          inner join supplier
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_totalprice >= supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (orders.o_clerk = orders.o_orderpriority)
        inner join region
        on (orders.o_shippriority = region.r_regionkey )
      on (orders.o_shippriority < orders.o_custkey)
    on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= lineitem.l_extendedprice)
where region.r_regionkey <= nation.n_nationkey
limit 52;

  customer.c_nationkey
from 
  supplier
          inner join region
          on (supplier.s_phone = region.r_name )
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey < partsupp.ps_suppkey)
      inner join orders
          inner join supplier
            inner join partsupp
              inner join partsupp
                inner join customer
                on (partsupp.ps_partkey = customer.c_custkey )
              on (partsupp.ps_partkey >= partsupp.ps_availqty)
            on (customer.c_mktsegment <= customer.c_phone)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join customer
            inner join lineitem
              inner join region
              on (lineitem.l_quantity >= lineitem.l_extendedprice)
            on (region.r_name = lineitem.l_shipmode)
          inner join supplier
            inner join nation
            on (nation.n_regionkey > supplier.s_nationkey)
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice < lineitem.l_tax)
        on (lineitem.l_tax >= orders.o_totalprice)
      on (orders.o_orderdate >= lineitem.l_shipdate)
    inner join region
    on (nation.n_comment is not NULL)
where partsupp.ps_availqty is NULL
