      inner join nation
      on (part.p_brand = nation.n_name )
    inner join partsupp
      inner join supplier
        inner join orders
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_custkey < orders.o_shippriority)
          inner join nation
          on (customer.c_phone > customer.c_phone)
        on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)

    on (supplier.s_name is NULL)

select

        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_quantity < part.p_retailprice)
      inner join customer
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey)
          inner join nation
          on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
        inner join region
        on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
      on (customer.c_mktsegment > customer.c_phone)
    inner join partsupp
            inner join region
            on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= region.r_regionkey)
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_shipmode = lineitem.l_returnflag)
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct >= lineitem.l_shipmode)

    on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct is NULL)

    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz))
from 
  supplier
      inner join region
        inner join customer
          inner join customer
            inner join nation
              inner join partsupp
                inner join partsupp
                on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
              on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = partsupp.ps_partkey)
            on (nation.n_name = customer.c_mktsegment)
          on (nation.n_regionkey >= customer.c_custkey)
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= customer.c_custkey)
    inner join orders
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey )
      inner join partsupp
      on (orders.o_totalprice < partsupp.ps_supplycost)

select

  lineitem.l_linenumber, 
  supplier.s_name,

  max(
    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz))
from 
  lineitem
      inner join supplier
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate <= lineitem.l_shipdate)
    inner join customer
        inner join orders
            inner join supplier
            on (orders.o_orderpriority >= orders.o_clerk)
          inner join supplier
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_totalprice > supplier.s_acctbal)
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
          on (orders.o_orderpriority < orders.o_orderstatus)
        on (orders.o_totalprice <= supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join supplier
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_name = supplier.s_name)
      on (orders.o_shippriority >= supplier.s_nationkey)
    on (lineitem.l_commitdate = lineitem.l_receiptdate)
where orders.o_orderkey is NULL

      on (supplier.s_phone = region.r_name )
    inner join partsupp
          inner join partsupp
            inner join lineitem
            on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = lineitem.l_discount)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = lineitem.l_quantity )
        inner join part
        on (part.p_container < lineitem.l_returnflag)
      inner join nation
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_acctbal >= customer.c_acctbal)
      on (part.p_brand > lineitem.l_linestatus)
    on (customer.c_phone is not NULL)

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_name, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)), 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct, 
  min(
    cast(supplier.s_acctbal as "numeric")), 
  max(
    cast(orders.o_clerk as bpchar))
from 
  nation
          inner join orders
          on (nation.n_comment = orders.o_comment )
        inner join customer
          inner join part
              inner join customer
              on (part.p_retailprice < customer.c_acctbal)
            inner join lineitem
            on (part.p_size <= customer.c_nationkey)
          on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct > lineitem.l_linestatus)
        on (orders.o_orderstatus = part.p_mfgr )
      inner join partsupp
              inner join supplier
              on (partsupp.ps_comment = supplier.s_address )
            inner join lineitem
            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_acctbal = lineitem.l_discount)
        inner join partsupp
            inner join partsupp
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          inner join part
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (lineitem.l_tax < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (lineitem.l_shipdate = lineitem.l_shipdate )
    inner join region
    on (orders.o_orderkey = region.r_regionkey )
where lineitem.l_tax < lineitem.l_extendedprice

              inner join lineitem

select  
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  part.p_name, 
  part.p_size, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  max(
    cast(partsupp.ps_partkey as int4))
from 
  lineitem
    inner join partsupp
            inner join region
                inner join partsupp
                on (partsupp.ps_availqty <= region.r_regionkey)
              inner join lineitem
              on (partsupp.ps_availqty = lineitem.l_orderkey )
            on (lineitem.l_shipmode > lineitem.l_shipmode)
          inner join part
                  inner join nation
                  on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
                inner join lineitem
                on (lineitem.l_shipmode <= part.p_brand)
              inner join orders
                inner join nation
                on (orders.o_totalprice <= orders.o_totalprice)
              on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)
            inner join customer
              inner join supplier
              on (supplier.s_phone < supplier.s_name)
            on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_commitdate)
          on (customer.c_acctbal = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join part
                  inner join part
                  on (part.p_size > part.p_size)
                inner join part
                on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
              inner join part
              on (part.p_mfgr <= part.p_mfgr)
            inner join customer
            on (part.p_type = customer.c_name )
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderpriority <= orders.o_orderpriority)
        on (part.p_brand > part.p_container)
      inner join nation
      on (customer.c_mktsegment > orders.o_orderpriority)
    on (part.p_brand is NULL)
where customer.c_mktsegment is not NULL
limit 125;

select

from 
  partsupp
        inner join region
        on (region.r_name < region.r_name)
      inner join part
      on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    inner join orders
          inner join region
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_mktsegment = customer.c_phone)
          on (customer.c_mktsegment >= region.r_name)
        inner join supplier
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
          inner join partsupp
            inner join customer
            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= partsupp.ps_suppkey)
          on (supplier.s_name <= customer.c_mktsegment)
        on (customer.c_nationkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
      inner join orders
            inner join part
            on (orders.o_custkey = orders.o_custkey)
          inner join part
          on (part.p_mfgr >= part.p_container)
        inner join customer
        on (part.p_partkey = customer.c_custkey )
      on (customer.c_name = part.p_name )
    on (supplier.s_address is NULL)
where orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate;

          inner join partsupp
            inner join region
            on (partsupp.ps_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey)
          on (part.p_mfgr > part.p_container)
        inner join customer
          inner join region
          on (customer.c_custkey <= region.r_regionkey)
        on (part.p_size > part.p_partkey)
      on (part.p_container > customer.c_mktsegment)
    inner join part
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join partsupp
        on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join part
      on (orders.o_clerk > part.p_container)
    on (orders.o_totalprice = orders.o_totalprice )
where orders.o_totalprice is NULL
limit 46;
nl: What are the p_partkey, total intervals, maximum values, and names of parts that have a null total price, along with their corresponding region keys, comments, and supplier keys?

sql:

  lineitem.l_extendedprice
from 
  lineitem
      inner join partsupp
        inner join nation
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (lineitem.l_shipmode >= lineitem.l_shipmode)
    inner join region
        inner join part
        on (part.p_retailprice <= part.p_retailprice)
      inner join part
      on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
    on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate)
where lineitem.l_shipinstruct >= part.p_brand
limit 66;
nl: What are the available quantities, supplier keys, region keys, and comments for each region, along with the extended prices of items shipped to that region?

                on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = lineitem.l_discount)
              inner join partsupp
              on (lineitem.l_shipmode > lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          inner join orders
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)

sql:
select

    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  customer.c_phone, 
  partsupp.ps_comment
from

        inner join supplier
          inner join region
          on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty > region.r_regionkey)
      inner join customer
        inner join part
          inner join nation
            inner join partsupp
            on (nation.n_name > nation.n_name)
          on (part.p_partkey = nation.n_nationkey )
        on (nation.n_name > part.p_container)
      on (partsupp.ps_availqty = customer.c_custkey )
    inner join region
        inner join part
          inner join partsupp
              inner join partsupp
              on (partsupp.ps_suppkey > partsupp.ps_suppkey)
            inner join partsupp
            on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= partsupp.ps_availqty)
          on (part.p_mfgr < part.p_container)
        on (part.p_retailprice <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      inner join part
      on (partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey )

where partsupp.ps_comment is not NULL

    inner join supplier
            inner join orders
                inner join region
                on (orders.o_orderkey > region.r_regionkey)
              inner join part
              on (region.r_regionkey = part.p_partkey )
            on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
          inner join customer
          on (orders.o_shippriority = region.r_regionkey)
        inner join customer
          inner join region
            inner join part
            on (region.r_comment = part.p_name )
          on (customer.c_acctbal <= part.p_retailprice)
        on (supplier.s_nationkey = part.p_partkey )
      inner join customer
      on (part.p_brand <= part.p_brand)
    on (orders.o_orderkey is NULL)
where region.r_regionkey is NULL;

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_shipmode, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  lineitem.l_orderkey, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)), 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8))
from 
  partsupp
      inner join supplier
          inner join lineitem
          on (supplier.s_address = lineitem.l_comment )
        inner join nation
            inner join partsupp
            on (nation.n_name <= nation.n_name)
          inner join supplier
            inner join nation
            on (supplier.s_nationkey = supplier.s_nationkey)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal )
      on (supplier.s_name = nation.n_name)
    inner join partsupp
        inner join part
          inner join partsupp
            inner join partsupp
              inner join lineitem
              on (lineitem.l_linestatus >= lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
            on (lineitem.l_extendedprice > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (part.p_brand = lineitem.l_returnflag )
        on (part.p_partkey > partsupp.ps_availqty)
      inner join part
          inner join supplier
          on (part.p_retailprice = supplier.s_acctbal)
        inner join supplier
          inner join lineitem
          on (supplier.s_name <= lineitem.l_linestatus)
        on (lineitem.l_suppkey >= supplier.s_nationkey)
      on (part.p_mfgr < lineitem.l_linestatus)
    on (nation.n_comment is not NULL)
where part.p_brand is NULL;

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  part.p_name
from 
  supplier
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_phone >= supplier.s_phone)
      inner join nation
      on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join nation
              inner join supplier
              on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
            inner join region
              inner join part
              on (region.r_comment = part.p_name )
            on (supplier.s_acctbal <= part.p_retailprice)
          inner join supplier
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (supplier.s_phone < part.p_container)
        inner join supplier
            inner join nation
              inner join customer
                inner join orders
                on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
              on (nation.n_nationkey = orders.o_orderkey )
            on (supplier.s_phone = orders.o_orderstatus )
          inner join nation
          on (orders.o_comment = nation.n_comment )
        on (supplier.s_name < nation.n_name)
      inner join orders
        inner join part
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderstatus < part.p_brand)
        on (orders.o_totalprice < orders.o_totalprice)
      on (nation.n_name = orders.o_orderstatus )
    on (nation.n_regionkey is NULL)
where region.r_regionkey is NULL;

        inner join partsupp

      inner join customer
            inner join nation
            on (customer.c_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey )
          inner join nation
          on (customer.c_nationkey >= customer.c_nationkey)
        inner join partsupp
        on (nation.n_regionkey = nation.n_regionkey)
      on (nation.n_regionkey = nation.n_nationkey )
    inner join supplier
      inner join part
        inner join customer
          inner join region
          on (customer.c_custkey <= customer.c_custkey)
        on (part.p_container = customer.c_phone )
      on (customer.c_acctbal < customer.c_acctbal)
    on (customer.c_nationkey = region.r_regionkey )

sql:
select  
  sum(

  customer.c_custkey,

    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)),

    cast(cast(null as timestamptz) as timestamptz)), 
  nation.n_comment, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  supplier.s_comment
from 
  nation
      inner join customer
        inner join supplier
          inner join supplier
              inner join customer
              on (supplier.s_name = customer.c_phone )
            inner join orders
            on (supplier.s_comment = orders.o_comment )
          on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
        on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
      on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join nation
    on (orders.o_shippriority is not NULL)
where orders.o_custkey is NULL;

sql:
select  
  customer.c_name, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  part.p_name, 
  supplier.s_name, 
  region.r_name, 
  part.p_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  supplier.s_name, 
  supplier.s_name, 
  part.p_type, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as text) as text)), 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8))
from 
  region
      inner join nation
        inner join part
          inner join partsupp
            inner join part
              inner join supplier
              on (part.p_size < supplier.s_nationkey)
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = part.p_retailprice )
          on (part.p_partkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= part.p_size)
      on (part.p_retailprice > supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join customer
          inner join customer
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
          on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
        inner join supplier
        on (customer.c_mktsegment = customer.c_mktsegment)
      inner join part
          inner join part
          on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
        inner join part
          inner join supplier
            inner join region
            on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (part.p_partkey >= supplier.s_nationkey)
        on (part.p_mfgr <= part.p_brand)
      on (part.p_size > orders.o_custkey)
    on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= orders.o_totalprice)
where part.p_size is NULL;

from

    inner join partsupp
          inner join customer
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < customer.c_acctbal)
        inner join lineitem
        on (customer.c_custkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
      inner join partsupp
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_receiptdate)

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_quantity, 
  part.p_type
from 
  nation
      inner join orders
          inner join part
              inner join partsupp
              on (part.p_container <= part.p_brand)
            inner join supplier
            on (part.p_partkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
          on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
        inner join lineitem
        on (part.p_brand >= orders.o_orderpriority)
      on (nation.n_nationkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
    inner join supplier
      inner join region
              inner join part
                inner join lineitem
                  inner join region
                  on (lineitem.l_partkey <= lineitem.l_suppkey)
                on (lineitem.l_receiptdate >= lineitem.l_commitdate)
              on (lineitem.l_orderkey <= region.r_regionkey)
            inner join customer
              inner join nation
              on (customer.c_custkey <= nation.n_nationkey)
            on (lineitem.l_suppkey <= lineitem.l_suppkey)
          inner join orders
          on (lineitem.l_tax = orders.o_totalprice )
        inner join lineitem
          inner join part
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = lineitem.l_tax)
        on (lineitem.l_orderkey < part.p_partkey)
      on (lineitem.l_discount < lineitem.l_quantity)
    on (customer.c_nationkey is NULL)
where partsupp.ps_availqty is not NULL;

sql:

  max(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4))
from 
  partsupp
    inner join lineitem
          inner join partsupp
          on (lineitem.l_linenumber < partsupp.ps_suppkey)
        inner join region
              inner join customer
              on (region.r_name = customer.c_phone )
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_mktsegment > customer.c_mktsegment)
          inner join region
          on (customer.c_nationkey <= customer.c_custkey)
        on (customer.c_phone < region.r_name)
      inner join partsupp
        inner join part
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)
    on (customer.c_phone <= customer.c_mktsegment)
where partsupp.ps_availqty is NULL
limit 77;

  lineitem.l_extendedprice, 
  lineitem.l_linenumber
from

        inner join partsupp

where partsupp.ps_suppkey is NULL

sql:
select  
  part.p_size, 
  nation.n_name, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as tid) as tid)), 
  part.p_size, 
  lineitem.l_linestatus
from 
  nation
    inner join lineitem
      inner join nation
        inner join region
          inner join part
          on (part.p_container <= part.p_brand)
        on (nation.n_regionkey > part.p_size)
      on (lineitem.l_orderkey = part.p_partkey )
    on (part.p_retailprice is NULL)
where region.r_regionkey is NULL
limit 55;
nl: What are the sizes of parts, names of nations, and statuses of lines for which there are no retail prices?

sql:
select  
  part.p_brand, 
  region.r_name, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  nation.n_name
from 
  part
      inner join customer
          inner join part
          on (part.p_mfgr <= part.p_container)
        inner join nation
        on (customer.c_nationkey > part.p_partkey)
      on (part.p_container <= part.p_brand)
    inner join region
          inner join supplier
            inner join region
            on (supplier.s_acctbal >= supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (region.r_regionkey >= region.r_regionkey)
        inner join region
        on (supplier.s_phone = region.r_name)
      inner join supplier
      on (supplier.s_phone > region.r_name)
    on (nation.n_name = region.r_name )
where customer.c_name is not NULL;
nl: What are the brands, regions, and nations of parts that have a manufacturer, container, and nation key, along with their minimum and maximum values?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  sum(
    cast(lineitem.l_tax as "numeric")), 
  part.p_brand
from 
  partsupp
        inner join part
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty = part.p_partkey )
      inner join part
          inner join part
          on (part.p_partkey >= part.p_partkey)
        inner join part
            inner join customer
            on (part.p_retailprice > customer.c_acctbal)
          inner join part
          on (customer.c_address = part.p_name )
        on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice )
      on (part.p_retailprice >= part.p_retailprice)
    inner join partsupp
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_phone > supplier.s_phone)
        inner join customer
          inner join lineitem
            inner join region
              inner join partsupp
              on (partsupp.ps_availqty < partsupp.ps_partkey)
            on (lineitem.l_partkey < lineitem.l_orderkey)
          on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct >= lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
        on (customer.c_mktsegment < supplier.s_phone)
      inner join customer
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_mktsegment < customer.c_phone)
        inner join region
        on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
      on (supplier.s_name >= lineitem.l_linestatus)
    on (customer.c_acctbal is not NULL)
where part.p_name is NULL
limit 133;
nl: What are the return flags, available quantities, supply costs, average values, total taxes, and brands of parts that have no retail price or name?

sql:
select  
  part.p_brand, 
  part.p_comment, 
  part.p_comment
from 
  part
    inner join supplier
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join part
            inner join region
              inner join partsupp
              on (region.r_regionkey > partsupp.ps_suppkey)
            on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
          inner join part
          on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_commitdate = lineitem.l_shipdate)
      on (part.p_retailprice <= lineitem.l_tax)
    on (part.p_partkey > region.r_regionkey)
where part.p_retailprice is NULL
limit 55;
nl: What are the brands, comments, and comments of parts that have no retail price?

sql:

  supplier.s_nationkey,

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_phone, 
  partsupp.ps_comment,

    cast(cast(null as text) as text)), 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost,

  partsupp.ps_suppkey
from 
  part
      inner join region
      on (region.r_regionkey >= part.p_size)
    inner join part
      inner join supplier
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
      on (part.p_type = partsupp.ps_comment )

      inner join partsupp

sql:
select  
  nation.n_name, 
  part.p_size, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  supplier.s_acctbal
from 
  partsupp
        inner join supplier
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty = supplier.s_suppkey)
      inner join orders
      on (supplier.s_acctbal <= orders.o_totalprice)
    inner join supplier
            inner join orders
            on (supplier.s_acctbal = orders.o_totalprice)
          inner join nation
            inner join orders
              inner join partsupp
              on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= orders.o_shippriority)
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (orders.o_totalprice > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join region
          inner join supplier
          on (region.r_comment = supplier.s_address )
        on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join part
      on (supplier.s_comment = part.p_name )
    on (nation.n_regionkey = supplier.s_nationkey)
where orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate
limit 93;

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey
from 
  region
      inner join customer
      on (customer.c_acctbal <= customer.c_acctbal)
    inner join partsupp
          inner join region
            inner join lineitem
              inner join nation
              on (lineitem.l_shipmode < nation.n_name)
            on (lineitem.l_tax = lineitem.l_discount)
          on (lineitem.l_commitdate = lineitem.l_receiptdate)
        inner join supplier
            inner join supplier
                  inner join orders
                  on (orders.o_orderstatus <= orders.o_clerk)
                inner join part
                on (supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
              inner join lineitem
              on (supplier.s_acctbal >= part.p_retailprice)
            on (supplier.s_comment = part.p_name )
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_acctbal >= supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (part.p_mfgr < orders.o_orderstatus)
      inner join supplier
          inner join orders
                inner join nation
                on (orders.o_totalprice <= orders.o_totalprice)
              inner join lineitem
              on (nation.n_regionkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_phone >= lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
          on (lineitem.l_orderkey <= lineitem.l_orderkey)
        inner join customer
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_nationkey <= customer.c_custkey)
        on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct < customer.c_mktsegment)
      on (lineitem.l_tax >= lineitem.l_discount)
    on (partsupp.ps_availqty is not NULL)
where part.p_partkey is not NULL
limit 145;

where region.r_name is NULL

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_name, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  customer.c_comment, 
  part.p_type, 
  orders.o_custkey
from 
  supplier
      inner join partsupp
      on (supplier.s_comment = partsupp.ps_comment )
    inner join lineitem
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_totalprice > lineitem.l_quantity)
            inner join lineitem
              inner join customer
              on (lineitem.l_orderkey >= lineitem.l_orderkey)
            on (customer.c_custkey > lineitem.l_suppkey)
          inner join customer
          on (lineitem.l_partkey > lineitem.l_orderkey)
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_orderkey >= customer.c_nationkey)
      inner join region
        inner join orders
            inner join region
            on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
          inner join supplier
            inner join part
              inner join supplier
              on (supplier.s_suppkey <= part.p_partkey)
            on (supplier.s_name <= supplier.s_name)
          on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
        on (supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
      on (supplier.s_phone = orders.o_orderpriority)
    on (customer.c_comment is not NULL)
where orders.o_orderdate > lineitem.l_commitdate;

    inner join part

              inner join part
                inner join nation
                on (part.p_size > nation.n_nationkey)
              on (orders.o_clerk >= nation.n_name)
            on (nation.n_nationkey = orders.o_orderkey)
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_discount >= part.p_retailprice)
      inner join lineitem
      on (lineitem.l_linenumber >= orders.o_orderkey)
    on (orders.o_orderdate is not NULL)

nl: What are the minimum and maximum values, along with some other details, for customers who have not paid their bills in full?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_receiptdate, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as xid8) as xid8)), 
  lineitem.l_suppkey, 
  lineitem.l_partkey, 
  part.p_comment, 
  part.p_size, 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  lineitem.l_tax, 
  part.p_type, 
  part.p_size, 
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  part.p_brand, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  lineitem.l_comment
from 
  lineitem
      inner join part
        inner join part

  orders.o_comment
from

          inner join partsupp

          on (lineitem.l_quantity >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)

        on (lineitem.l_shipdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate)
      inner join orders
      on (lineitem.l_returnflag = orders.o_orderstatus )
    inner join lineitem
            inner join partsupp
            on (lineitem.l_discount >= lineitem.l_extendedprice)
          inner join nation
          on (lineitem.l_linenumber < lineitem.l_linenumber)
        inner join partsupp
        on (nation.n_nationkey > partsupp.ps_suppkey)
      inner join supplier
      on (lineitem.l_discount >= lineitem.l_discount)
    on (nation.n_name = nation.n_name)
where customer.c_acctbal > lineitem.l_tax;

          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
        on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)

            inner join partsupp

        on (partsupp.ps_availqty = partsupp.ps_suppkey)

  nation.n_name,

  max(
    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp"))
from

        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join lineitem
      on (supplier.s_nationkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
    inner join part
        inner join nation
            inner join nation
            on (nation.n_regionkey > nation.n_nationkey)
          inner join region
          on (nation.n_comment = region.r_comment )
        on (part.p_mfgr >= part.p_mfgr)
      inner join supplier
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_returnflag <= supplier.s_name)
      on (part.p_mfgr = supplier.s_name )

where supplier.s_nationkey is not NULL

        inner join region
          inner join partsupp
            inner join nation
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (nation.n_nationkey >= nation.n_regionkey)
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty >= part.p_partkey)
      inner join nation
        inner join lineitem
        on (nation.n_name = lineitem.l_returnflag )
      on (lineitem.l_discount = lineitem.l_extendedprice)
    inner join region
          inner join region
          on (region.r_regionkey > region.r_regionkey)
        inner join orders
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_partkey >= orders.o_custkey)
        on (lineitem.l_quantity = lineitem.l_tax)
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_clerk < orders.o_clerk)
    on (partsupp.ps_supplycost is NULL)
where lineitem.l_discount is not NULL
limit 160;

            inner join region

          on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)

      inner join lineitem

select  
  max(
    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as timestamptz) as timestamptz)), 
  lineitem.l_extendedprice, 
  customer.c_comment, 
  customer.c_nationkey
from 
  part
    inner join customer
        inner join orders
        on (customer.c_mktsegment = orders.o_orderstatus )
      inner join orders
              inner join part
              on (orders.o_shippriority = part.p_partkey )
            inner join region
              inner join lineitem
                inner join partsupp
                on (lineitem.l_orderkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
              on (lineitem.l_commitdate >= lineitem.l_commitdate)
            on (part.p_partkey >= region.r_regionkey)
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = lineitem.l_tax)
        inner join lineitem
          inner join partsupp
                inner join lineitem
                on (lineitem.l_shipdate < lineitem.l_shipdate)
              inner join customer
                inner join supplier
                on (supplier.s_acctbal < customer.c_acctbal)
              on (lineitem.l_quantity >= lineitem.l_discount)
            inner join lineitem
            on (lineitem.l_receiptdate >= lineitem.l_receiptdate)
          on (lineitem.l_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty = customer.c_custkey )
      on (partsupp.ps_suppkey > lineitem.l_linenumber)
    on (lineitem.l_suppkey > lineitem.l_suppkey)
where part.p_comment is not NULL;

              inner join part

            inner join nation
              inner join customer
              on (customer.c_phone < customer.c_phone)
            on (lineitem.l_extendedprice < lineitem.l_tax)
          inner join nation
          on (customer.c_acctbal > part.p_retailprice)
        inner join partsupp
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_phone <= supplier.s_name)
        on (part.p_name = partsupp.ps_comment )
      inner join region
      on (lineitem.l_extendedprice >= customer.c_acctbal)

          inner join orders
          on (lineitem.l_returnflag = orders.o_orderstatus )
        inner join part
          inner join supplier
            inner join region
              inner join partsupp
              on (region.r_name >= region.r_name)
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (region.r_regionkey <= partsupp.ps_suppkey)
        on (lineitem.l_extendedprice <= supplier.s_acctbal)
      on (customer.c_comment = part.p_name )
    on (supplier.s_name is NULL)
where customer.c_phone is not NULL

            on (lineitem.l_extendedprice < lineitem.l_extendedprice)
          inner join customer
          on (lineitem.l_suppkey >= lineitem.l_linenumber)
        on (part.p_mfgr = part.p_container)
      on (lineitem.l_shipdate >= lineitem.l_receiptdate)
    inner join customer
    on (partsupp.ps_partkey >= lineitem.l_suppkey)
where customer.c_mktsegment >= lineitem.l_returnflag
limit 31;
nl: What are the minimum, market segments of customers, and nations that meet certain conditions?

sql:
select  
  part.p_type, 
  region.r_comment, 
  min(
    cast(lineitem.l_commitdate as date)), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  part.p_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  supplier.s_address, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  part.p_partkey
from 
  part
          inner join region
            inner join nation
              inner join supplier
                inner join lineitem
                on (supplier.s_address = lineitem.l_comment )
              on (lineitem.l_tax < supplier.s_acctbal)
            on (lineitem.l_commitdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)
          on (lineitem.l_quantity < supplier.s_acctbal)
        inner join partsupp
          inner join customer
          on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = customer.c_custkey )
        on (lineitem.l_tax = supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join region
          inner join partsupp
          on (partsupp.ps_availqty <= partsupp.ps_suppkey)
        inner join supplier
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_custkey <= customer.c_nationkey)
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= supplier.s_acctbal)
      on (partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_orderkey)
    inner join part
    on (part.p_mfgr = part.p_mfgr )
where nation.n_nationkey is NULL
limit 80;
nl: What are the types of parts, comments from regions and nations, earliest dates, and other details about specific parts, suppliers, customers, and line items that have no nation key?

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  part.p_name, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  part.p_brand, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  orders.o_comment, 
  part.p_partkey, 
  part.p_type, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  part.p_comment
from 
  customer
        inner join part
              inner join part
              on (part.p_container < part.p_mfgr)
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_clerk <= orders.o_orderstatus)
          inner join orders
          on (part.p_size > orders.o_custkey)
        on (part.p_size <= orders.o_shippriority)
      inner join lineitem
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < lineitem.l_extendedprice)
      on (part.p_size = customer.c_nationkey)
    inner join lineitem
    on (lineitem.l_shipdate < orders.o_orderdate)
where partsupp.ps_availqty < orders.o_custkey;
nl: What are the part keys, names, and brands of all parts that have a supplier with available quantity less than the customer key?

sql:
select  
  part.p_partkey, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  supplier.s_name, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8))
from 
  nation
    inner join part
      inner join supplier
      on (part.p_container = part.p_brand)
    on (part.p_container is NULL)
where part.p_size is not NULL
limit 144;
nl: What are the part keys, phone numbers, and names of suppliers that provide parts with a size, along with their average rating?

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  count(*), 
  region.r_name, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  part.p_name, 
  part.p_type
from 
  customer
    inner join lineitem
        inner join partsupp
          inner join region
          on (region.r_regionkey < partsupp.ps_suppkey)
        on (lineitem.l_linestatus > lineitem.l_shipmode)
      inner join part
      on (lineitem.l_partkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
    on (lineitem.l_orderkey is NULL)
where customer.c_acctbal is not NULL;
nl: What are the supply costs, counts, and details of regions, customers, suppliers, parts, and their types for customers with non-zero account balances?

sql:
select  
  region.r_comment, 
  part.p_brand, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  part.p_type, 
  supplier.s_address, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  supplier.s_name
from 
  supplier
    inner join lineitem
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_nationkey <= lineitem.l_partkey)
      inner join region
            inner join nation
            on (region.r_name = nation.n_name )
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
        inner join customer
            inner join part
            on (customer.c_mktsegment = part.p_mfgr )
          inner join orders
              inner join lineitem
              on (orders.o_orderkey <= orders.o_shippriority)
            inner join supplier
            on (lineitem.l_linenumber >= lineitem.l_suppkey)
          on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
        on (region.r_regionkey = part.p_partkey )
      on (supplier.s_phone <= supplier.s_name)
    on (orders.o_clerk is NULL)
where supplier.s_acctbal >= lineitem.l_extendedprice
limit 107;
nl: What are the comments, brands, phone numbers, types, addresses, and order priorities of suppliers that have a certain level of account balance, along with their customers' phone numbers, and what region they operate in?

sql:
select  
  part.p_name
from 
  part
    inner join region
        inner join part
        on (part.p_partkey > region.r_regionkey)
      inner join customer
        inner join supplier
            inner join orders
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
            on (orders.o_clerk <= orders.o_clerk)
          inner join lineitem
          on (orders.o_orderdate >= lineitem.l_commitdate)
        on (orders.o_totalprice >= lineitem.l_tax)
      on (lineitem.l_extendedprice < customer.c_acctbal)
    on (part.p_partkey = orders.o_orderkey )
where customer.c_custkey is not NULL
limit 113;
nl: What are the names of parts that have been ordered by customers who have a balance greater than the total price paid for those parts, and which regions these parts come from?

sql:

            inner join nation
            on (part.p_retailprice > lineitem.l_discount)
          inner join orders
          on (lineitem.l_receiptdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join customer
        on (orders.o_orderkey >= orders.o_orderkey)
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate <= lineitem.l_receiptdate)

  supplier.s_name, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty
from

      inner join supplier

nl: What are the part keys, earliest timestamps, total supplier counts, supply costs, account balances, names, and available quantities for suppliers with no outstanding balance?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  min(
    cast(lineitem.l_shipdate as date)), 
  part.p_size, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct
from 
  nation
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_quantity = lineitem.l_quantity)
      inner join part
            inner join region
            on (part.p_partkey = region.r_regionkey)
          inner join orders
            inner join nation
              inner join part
              on (nation.n_name = part.p_mfgr )
            on (orders.o_shippriority = nation.n_nationkey )
          on (orders.o_custkey <= part.p_size)
        inner join nation
            inner join orders
              inner join part
              on (part.p_container = orders.o_orderpriority)
            on (nation.n_nationkey = part.p_partkey)
          inner join partsupp
          on (nation.n_name > part.p_container)
        on (part.p_retailprice = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (orders.o_custkey < region.r_regionkey)
    inner join supplier
    on (part.p_mfgr > orders.o_orderstatus)
where nation.n_comment is not NULL
limit 48;

from

    inner join customer
                inner join region
                on (customer.c_nationkey = region.r_regionkey )

              on (region.r_regionkey < region.r_regionkey)

          inner join part
          on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= region.r_regionkey)
        inner join partsupp
        on (orders.o_orderkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )

from

      inner join supplier
      on (orders.o_clerk = supplier.s_name)

          inner join customer

            on (orders.o_orderpriority < orders.o_orderpriority)
          on (customer.c_custkey >= orders.o_custkey)

          on (lineitem.l_discount > lineitem.l_quantity)
        on (lineitem.l_extendedprice <= lineitem.l_tax)
      on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= lineitem.l_quantity)
    on (part.p_size is NULL)

          inner join partsupp

        inner join partsupp
        on (lineitem.l_linestatus >= lineitem.l_shipmode)
      on (nation.n_nationkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )

    on (lineitem.l_linenumber = lineitem.l_orderkey )
where customer.c_nationkey is NULL

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  lineitem.l_shipdate
from 
  supplier
      inner join supplier
        inner join nation
            inner join partsupp
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          inner join nation
          on (partsupp.ps_partkey = nation.n_nationkey )
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < supplier.s_acctbal)
      on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= supplier.s_nationkey)
    inner join customer
        inner join lineitem
        on (customer.c_mktsegment <= lineitem.l_linestatus)
      inner join region
          inner join partsupp
          on (region.r_name = region.r_name)
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
      on (supplier.s_nationkey = partsupp.ps_partkey)
    on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
where supplier.s_comment is not NULL;

sql:
select  
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  part.p_container, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  supplier.s_comment
from 
  nation
            inner join part
                inner join nation
                on (nation.n_nationkey >= part.p_size)
              inner join partsupp
                inner join partsupp
                on (partsupp.ps_partkey > partsupp.ps_availqty)
              on (nation.n_name = part.p_container)
            on (nation.n_name <= part.p_brand)
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_phone >= part.p_mfgr)
        inner join partsupp
          inner join supplier
            inner join customer
            on (supplier.s_nationkey = customer.c_custkey)
          on (customer.c_custkey >= customer.c_custkey)
        on (customer.c_acctbal >= supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join orders
              inner join nation
              on (orders.o_totalprice < orders.o_totalprice)
            inner join part
            on (orders.o_clerk <= part.p_brand)
          inner join part
            inner join orders
            on (part.p_container = orders.o_orderstatus )
          on (orders.o_totalprice = part.p_retailprice)
        inner join lineitem
        on (orders.o_totalprice >= lineitem.l_discount)
      on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = orders.o_orderkey )
    inner join supplier
      inner join region
          inner join nation
          on (nation.n_nationkey < region.r_regionkey)
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_name < nation.n_name)
      on (supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
    on (partsupp.ps_supplycost is NULL)
where nation.n_name < lineitem.l_shipmode
limit 164;
nl: What is the sum of null values, along with information about containers, regions, available quantities, and comments for suppliers that have a certain phone number?

sql:

        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
      on (supplier.s_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
    inner join partsupp

select  
  part.p_size, 
  part.p_name,

    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")), 
  part.p_partkey
from 
  nation
        inner join region
        on (region.r_name > region.r_name)
      inner join lineitem
      on (lineitem.l_shipdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate)
    inner join customer
        inner join nation
        on (customer.c_phone >= customer.c_mktsegment)
      inner join region
        inner join part
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_name <= part.p_container)
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_phone <= supplier.s_phone)
        on (supplier.s_nationkey = supplier.s_suppkey)
      on (part.p_retailprice < supplier.s_acctbal)
    on (nation.n_nationkey = nation.n_regionkey)
where supplier.s_nationkey is not NULL

sql:
select  
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  max(
    cast(lineitem.l_receiptdate as date)), 
  count(*), 
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  lineitem.l_orderkey, 
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  lineitem.l_linestatus, 
  orders.o_comment, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  lineitem.l_discount
from 
  orders
    inner join orders
        inner join nation
        on (orders.o_shippriority <= nation.n_regionkey)
      inner join partsupp
        inner join orders
          inner join part
              inner join supplier
                inner join customer
                on (supplier.s_name > customer.c_phone)
              on (part.p_retailprice > customer.c_acctbal)
            inner join lineitem
            on (part.p_retailprice = lineitem.l_quantity )
          on (customer.c_custkey = customer.c_nationkey)
        on (lineitem.l_linestatus < part.p_container)
      on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
    on (lineitem.l_tax < lineitem.l_discount)
where partsupp.ps_supplycost <= part.p_retailprice
limit 178;

sql:
select  
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  min(
    cast(orders.o_shippriority as int4)), 
  customer.c_comment, 
  part.p_name, 
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz)), 
  customer.c_phone
from 
  customer
      inner join nation
            inner join orders
              inner join part
              on (orders.o_orderpriority < orders.o_orderpriority)
            on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
          inner join lineitem
            inner join customer
            on (lineitem.l_receiptdate = lineitem.l_commitdate)
          on (orders.o_orderkey = customer.c_custkey )
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_acctbal = lineitem.l_quantity)
      on (orders.o_clerk >= orders.o_orderstatus)
    inner join supplier
      inner join part
      on (supplier.s_phone > part.p_container)
    on (supplier.s_acctbal <= customer.c_acctbal)
where supplier.s_name is not NULL
limit 142;

sql:
select  
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  lineitem.l_receiptdate, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as timestamptz) as timestamptz)), 
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  lineitem.l_quantity, 
  lineitem.l_linenumber, 
  supplier.s_address
from 
  part
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_shippriority >= orders.o_custkey)
      inner join part
        inner join nation
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_custkey = customer.c_custkey)
        on (part.p_retailprice >= part.p_retailprice)
      on (part.p_partkey = customer.c_nationkey)
    inner join lineitem
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_tax = lineitem.l_quantity )
        inner join supplier
          inner join orders
            inner join region
            on (orders.o_clerk < orders.o_clerk)
          on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (supplier.s_nationkey = lineitem.l_partkey)
      inner join lineitem
      on (orders.o_custkey <= lineitem.l_partkey)
    on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct > orders.o_clerk)
where lineitem.l_suppkey <= lineitem.l_partkey
limit 37;

sql:
select  
  region.r_name, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  customer.c_name
from 
  region
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      inner join supplier
      on (supplier.s_phone > supplier.s_name)
    inner join customer
          inner join partsupp
            inner join orders
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (customer.c_nationkey >= orders.o_custkey)
        inner join partsupp
            inner join region
            on (region.r_name >= region.r_name)
          inner join part
          on (part.p_brand >= part.p_container)
        on (customer.c_custkey = partsupp.ps_availqty)
      inner join supplier
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_mktsegment > customer.c_mktsegment)
      on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
    on (partsupp.ps_partkey is NULL)
where customer.c_mktsegment < region.r_name
limit 89;

sql:
select  
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  part.p_brand, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  part.p_type, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  part.p_mfgr,

from

      inner join supplier
      on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join part
        inner join nation
          inner join nation
          on (nation.n_regionkey >= nation.n_regionkey)
        on (nation.n_nationkey > part.p_size)
      inner join orders
        inner join supplier
          inner join part
            inner join partsupp
              inner join part
              on (partsupp.ps_comment = part.p_name )
            on (part.p_type = partsupp.ps_comment )
          on (part.p_brand < part.p_mfgr)
        on (supplier.s_name >= supplier.s_name)
      on (part.p_mfgr > part.p_brand)
    on (partsupp.ps_availqty is NULL)
where orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate

          inner join partsupp

            inner join supplier
            on (part.p_partkey <= supplier.s_suppkey)
          inner join region
          on (region.r_regionkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = supplier.s_acctbal )
      inner join supplier
          inner join region
          on (region.r_regionkey = supplier.s_nationkey)
        inner join nation

            on (orders.o_totalprice < orders.o_totalprice)
          on (nation.n_comment = region.r_comment )
        on (supplier.s_nationkey = orders.o_orderkey )

sql:
select  
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  part.p_container, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")),

nl: What are the names, part keys, and comments of parts that have a retail price equal to their supply cost, manufactured by a specific manufacturer, and do not have a container, along with the customer phone numbers and supplier information for these parts?

      inner join nation

sql:
select  
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4)), 
  part.p_name, 
  customer.c_name, 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  nation.n_name, 
  customer.c_name, 
  part.p_size, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  part.p_size, 
  nation.n_nationkey
from 
  customer
      inner join nation
          inner join orders
              inner join partsupp
              on (orders.o_totalprice > orders.o_totalprice)
            inner join nation
            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
          on (partsupp.ps_availqty >= orders.o_shippriority)
        inner join part
        on (part.p_container <= orders.o_orderstatus)
      on (orders.o_orderpriority <= orders.o_orderpriority)
    inner join part
      inner join part
        inner join region
        on (region.r_name = part.p_brand)
      on (part.p_retailprice >= part.p_retailprice)
    on (region.r_comment is NULL)
where orders.o_orderstatus is NULL
limit 90;
nl: What are the total prices, priorities, and other details of all orders that have no status, along with information about the customers, parts, suppliers, nations, and regions involved?

sql:
select  
  region.r_name, 
  supplier.s_name
from 
  supplier
    inner join partsupp
        inner join orders
          inner join nation
            inner join supplier
                inner join orders
                on (supplier.s_suppkey < supplier.s_nationkey)
              inner join region
              on (orders.o_shippriority >= region.r_regionkey)
            on (orders.o_totalprice > supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (orders.o_totalprice = orders.o_totalprice)
        on (region.r_regionkey = partsupp.ps_partkey)
      inner join region
      on (supplier.s_phone > orders.o_clerk)
    on (supplier.s_nationkey = region.r_regionkey )
where region.r_comment is NULL
limit 41;
nl: What are the names of regions and suppliers where there is no comment, and how many such regions and suppliers exist?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_address, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  nation.n_name, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  part.p_brand
from 
  part
      inner join partsupp
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_custkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey)
      on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
    inner join part
            inner join customer
            on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
          inner join nation
          on (part.p_comment = nation.n_comment )
        inner join supplier
        on (part.p_size > part.p_partkey)
      inner join supplier
        inner join supplier
              inner join nation
              on (nation.n_regionkey > nation.n_regionkey)
            inner join nation
                inner join nation
                on (nation.n_nationkey = nation.n_regionkey)
              inner join lineitem
                inner join supplier
                on (lineitem.l_shipdate >= lineitem.l_receiptdate)
              on (lineitem.l_linestatus <= lineitem.l_shipmode)
            on (nation.n_name = supplier.s_name)
          inner join part
          on (nation.n_comment = part.p_name )
        on (lineitem.l_linestatus < supplier.s_phone)
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate <= lineitem.l_commitdate)
    on (lineitem.l_commitdate = lineitem.l_shipdate)
where nation.n_name > lineitem.l_linestatus
limit 70;
nl: What are the addresses, account balances, countries, region keys, and brands of suppliers that have shipped parts to customers in a specific country, with orders received after a certain date?
